main event: An observer reported seeing a UFO multiple times between October 1959 and March 1960 in Elko, Nevada.
interesting points: The observer corresponded extensively regarding the sightings., The sightings occurred on multiple dates including 19 Oct 59 and various times in 1960., The observer interprets the sightings as objects from another world., The duration of each sighting was approximately one minute., A request was made to forward the negative of a print taken during one of the sightings.
